| Metric | Value |
|--------|-------|
| **Bid** | $${stock.bid.toFixed(2)} |
| **Ask** | $${stock.ask.toFixed(2)} |
| **Spread** | $${(stock.ask - stock.bid).toFixed(3)} (${(((stock.ask - stock.bid) / stock.ask) * 100).toFixed(2)}%) |

**Next Steps:**
