- [ ] Check earnings date (avoid if within 2 weeks)
- [ ] Analyze technical setup (support/resistance)

---
`
  )
  .join("\n")}

**üïê Last Updated:** ${new Date(data.timestamp).toLocaleTimeString()} ET

---

